What's ODENOS
==========================
ODENOS is a framework for developing SDN controller.
It is not SDN controller itself, but libraries (SDK).
ODENOS is implemented with Java, Python, and Ruby language.


How to use ODENOS
==========================
Please read "QUICKSTART.md" file.


Supported Hardware
==========================
- CPU: Intel x64 servers.(with compatible)
- Memory: >= 2GB


Supported Software
==========================
ODENOS can be compiled and run on Ubuntu 14.04 with JDK7.


Support
==========================
ODENOS Official site is <https://github.com/o3project/odenos>.


Development
==========================
Your contribution are very welcome, please submit your patch code using
github "Pull Requests".
If you find any bug, let us know by github's Issues page.
